The paper also discusses the use of auxiliary information, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). The concepts of logical depth and sophistication are also related to mathematical logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the ability of auxiliary information to solve the halting problem, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the paper also discusses the relation between the expressions of $(x, y)$, $(x)$ and $(y | x)$, which is related to data structures (cs.DS).
